The source code of "FFmpegKitNext", "FFmpeg" and external source packages
downloaded by "FFmpegKitNext" build scripts for this release is listed on
the following page:

https://github.com/arthenica/ffmpeg-kit-next/wiki/Source

"FFmpegKitNext" does not distribute ready-to-use binary packages. Build
outputs are produced locally by users from the published source code and the
source packages pinned by the build scripts.

